{"tid":2109124,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"西九地盤啲膠層只係睇工程進度 死都唔停工 草菅人命","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T06:18:26.000Z","uid":168081,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8c171030f8dccd79f2f6c1b874df036731e5f9","tid":2109124,"uid":168081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"依家日日逼人簽健康申報表，講真個個都話自己無接觸過確診人士，又唔係住嗰啲大廈嫁啦<br />\n個個日薪既，老虎蟹都話自己無事啦。<br />\n有啲覺得危險既就已經工都唔反。<br />\n好啦 簽左個表交左比衛生署就當無問題可以繼續進行工程<br />\n又叫人帶住個口罩開工，個個釘板扎鐵，地盤長期40度<br />\n唔好玩啦膠層，搞咁多嘢不如停工7日/14日算啦<br />\n比啲工人一黎有安心，二黎如果地盤一爆既到時咪輸仲多錢，不過反正都係叫唐英年同政府拎嫁啦<br />\n唉。<br />\n#首次發文吹下水"},{"pid":"f1aced8c2af91894289b6037702504907294ca23","tid":2109124,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb064329d8af41bee24321036dd925a8dbeaa116","tid":2109124,"uid":168081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1aced8c2af91894289b6037702504907294ca23","tid":2109124,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"我都知錢好緊要 但人命係咪真係咁低賤呢"},{"pid":"2d3ff4a7b03692126f6041c814ecdd49cee78d1e","tid":2109124,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"地盤新年後都冇停過"},{"pid":"b5bfb9e66188c44b7a1520b6be8383c1932c422d","tid":2109124,"uid":184370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金門垃圾開"},{"pid":"b2bc6ad06a468b297f1ad41dad2b708065bfe3e9","tid":2109124,"uid":168081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5bfb9e66188c44b7a1520b6be8383c1932c422d","tid":2109124,"uid":184370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金門垃圾開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:14:53.0